<div class="pros-list">
<h4>STRENGTHS</h4>
<ul>
  <li>✓ Industry standard — most agencies and CRMs integrate with it</li>
  <li>✓ Dynamic number insertion works seamlessly with HVAC websites</li>
  <li>✓ Call recording with AI-powered conversation intelligence</li>
  <li>✓ Native Google LSA integration</li>
